Dialogue: 100,0:00:06.23,0:00:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Battle!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.86,0:00:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some newcomers this time. If you please?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.11,0:00:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1410,1033)}It's Fafnir!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.16,0:00:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(475,1033)}Introduce me, too!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.70,0:00:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(945,1033)}Me too...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.49,0:00:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(945,1033)}Nah, never mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.62,0:00:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Some more fresh faces, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The fans were asking for one of them, \Nso I invited them over.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.41,0:00:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.37,0:00:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get started.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.09,0:00:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay, }I guess I can tag along.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.63,0:00:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Western!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, it's time for our showdown.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.64,0:00:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back-to-back, \Ncount off three steps, then shoot.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.64,0:00:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.64,0:00:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.64,0:00:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.69,0:00:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you shoot?!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:50.40,0:00:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to shoot\Nuntil we've counted to three!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.78,0:00:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't think I'd actually follow your rules, did you?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You crooked...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.70,0:01:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Saw it coming.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.37,0:01:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Count to three, then shoot.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.96,0:01:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.00,0:01:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.92,0:01:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.38,0:01:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad... you weren't... the one to die...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.93,0:01:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No snappy one-liner?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.51,0:01:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Ganryujima!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.31,0:01:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not coming.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:30.65,0:01:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We agreed to reenact the duel{ of Ganryujima} here.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.03,0:01:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he stood you up. Figures.{whatever, man}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.70,0:01:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.82,0:01:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. I got here five minutes ago.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.20,0:01:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you got an early start.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:40.95,0:01:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.83,0:01:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Kung Fu!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.21,0:01:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Tai Chi?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.59,0:01:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon RPG!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.31,0:02:07.94,Default,,0,0,10,,Please, just shut up.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,10,,Ah, that's over.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,10,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.48,Default,,0,0,10,,What, no item drops?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.48,0:02:15.74,Default,,0,0,10,,I mean, it was the final boss.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.11,Default,,0,0,10,,Well, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Battlefield!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.36,0:02:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it outside!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't had one proper battle yet.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what human battles are like?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.96,0:02:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to let loose?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.46,0:02:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good. Let's give our audience \Na proper battle between dragons!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.67,0:02:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get out of hand, I will stop you by force.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.48,0:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... See you next time, I guess.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible!{no, Nakamura, your delivery of this line is incredible}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You get used to it.